What is multipass?
--------------------

Multipassd is a daemon that orchestrates the creation, management and
maintenance of virtual machine and associated ubuntu images to simplify
development on various platforms such as OSX and Windows 10

Submodules
--------------------------------------
Make sure you update all the submodules under 3rd-party

git submodule update --init --recursive

Dependencies
---------------------------------------
gRPC has to be built from source, pull all the required submodules with:

    git submodule update --init --recursive

#zlib1g-dev is a hack, gRPC/third_party/zlib fails to build otherwise...
apt install cmake cmake-extras build-essential golang zlib1g-dev libprocess-cpp-dev google-mock


Building
---------------------------------------

Build and install gRPC first

    cd <multipass_root>
    mkdir build-grpc
    cd build-grpc
    cmake ../3rd-party/grpc
    make
    sudo make install

Then multipass

    cd <multipass_root>
    mkdir build-multipass
    cd build-multipass
    cmake ../
    make

Running daemon
---------------------------------------

   <multipass_root>/build-multipass/multipassd

   <multipass_root>/build-multipass/ubuntu launch (should pop up a qemu instance)


